Reasoning: The paper deals with the dynamics and control of abelian group codes, which are related to information theory and systems theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses controllability and observability properties, which are related to control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) another likely sub-category. The paper also uses concepts from dynamical systems (cs.DS), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and machine learning (cs.LG) in its analysis and examples.
